verbose_text: F43E2.6 siRNAs were modestly elevated in rde-1 mutants (p < = 0.004), suggesting that association with RDE-1 destabilizes them relative to other Argonautes they might interact with or that their production is elevated in the absence of rde-1 (XREF_FIG).
evidence: F43E2.6 siRNAs were modestly elevated in rde-1 mutants
